metadata.name: CAMALEOPARDA
metadata.description:
Artist: Arturo Zuñiga Vega

This artwork is Arturo’s genesis NFT. 

"CAMALEOPARDA" is the result of playing with one human and two animal parts, as well as a pop element. It gives rise to the universe of the famous "Camaladies" and is one of the artist's favorite creations and characters that captures the surprise, innocence and sensuality in such an exquisite creature.
